				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Casual player needing help<a name="67446"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 19 04 12:01 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey,
<br />

<br />
I don't have time for a full reply atm, but I'll give it a shot.  I am also a long time lurker and I actually registered just to reply to your post.
<br />

<br />
I also took a break but at 55.
<br />

<br />
You are at a perfect level to learn how to swarm kite in PoN.
<br />

<br />
That xp will be good to around 62 and will get you to 65 but not 66.  An added bonus is: they drop diamonds etc. 
<br />

<br />
I'd say once you get to be 65 you can try to get gruops in WoS or mebe RCod. (WAll of slaughter or Ruined cityof Dranik)  Both of those spots are reasonably good xp till 70. 
<br />

<br />
In terms of gear, you're gonna have to  be creative.  LDON was great and if they still have ldon groups around u are a great addition to most groups once you learn to pull.  
<br />

<br />
IF that won't work you can try buying some of the new OoW gear when the prices drop..and drop they will since the drops are very common.  Some of that is quite good.  
<br />

<br />
Another thought is buying some of the ok crafted items or perhaps some old ldon gear (nro breastplate for one..architects breastplate is name i think)
<br />

<br />
Ok gotta go sorry this is so disorganized.  I hope its helpful.
<br />

<br />
Q
<br />
</span></td>
