				<td colspan="2"><span>I would definately do a LOT of LDONs. They are fun (though a bit repetitive), and you can rackup some points for buying armour and such. There is some NICE armour for your level that sell for only 150.  Do some research on LDON merchants on this site and you can figure out your goals. 
<br />

<br />
At the mid 50s you will get maybe 1/3 to 1/2 of a level each trip. I have not been having much dificulty getting ldons still, even after OOW release. 
<br />

<br />
I was very poor up to level 63 or so, so I was in the same boat you are in now. That is why I did LDONs.. no money for decent items.
<br />

<br />
In my mid 50s I swarm kited in Nadox, but that requires run3. I was pulling about 500p per 3 hour period. I know there is a lot of places that do better .. but I like swarming.</span></td>
