He doesn't have GoD or OOW.
<br />

<br />
Personally my suggestion to you is somewhat along the lines of what I did.  Farm items you know you can.  Try farming Iksar hide mask I think you should be able to do it at your level may have to mez/heal for some of it.  (think the mob summons can't remember *shrug*).  The mask on drinal sold for 10k I think last time I played there.  The only problem with farming lore is you can only have 2 (one in shared bank one on your toon).  So if it doesn't sell fast on Drinal it may not be great for making any money.
