IF YOU GET GOD -- You can use the FT ability from the taskmaster (forget the correct named) just need to get points, don't spend money.  What I did is went to City of mist one evening cause I was bored, just raped the whole front of the city.  (The main courtyard, the &quot;stables&quot;? to the left and the temple thing to the right of entrance.)  Found some arm items and other stuff took it to taskmaster and was able to earn over 2-4k in points.  That should keep you going for quite some time.
<br />

