				<td colspan="2"><span>Wow thanks for all the advice guys.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />  I have been sorely tempted by the Architect's BP but wasn't sure if I should hold out for something more.  I will definitely have to learn how to swarm-kite and I might try putting more in AA's.  I have done...about 60 LDoN's I think and I quite enjoy them, when I can find people to do them with me.  One of the things I like best is that with the time limit I can say &quot;I need the computer for 90 minutes - 2 hours&quot; and know that I've done something without having camped the same bloody thing all day for nothing!  I think I'm a reasonable puller most of the time, although occasionally when soothe resists or some jerk is hiding behind a door I get a roomful - I have been able to salvage this through manic mezzing on more than one occasion though!
