				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Casual player needing help<a name="67566"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 20 04 9:59 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I like OoW's Dranic Scar 49-55..
<br />

<br />
For what its worth...and this isn't solo, mind you but boxing 4 50 to 52 toons (total group--self buffed, no c, no v), I make very good exp and about 500-1k per hour per toon in Dranik Scar. (not including as many as 3 named drops in a 3 hour period).
<br />

<br />
I would put a level 52 group's exp and loot up against POP zones like PoD and PoI. I think it compares very favorably (of course I have been there and done those, so I am looking for something a bit different as well).
<br />

<br />
A full group, say in the sw corner, can work non stop and, at least for me, exceed LDoN loot/exp as well.
<br />

<br />
The down side? (I am boxing) and it seems at least one toon has to face down or the hill side to avoid lag (the others are fine...go figure). In addition, it can take 10-30 secs to loot each mob because of the old sink beneath the surface bug...targetting dead mobs has proven difficult for me.
<br />

<br />
I haven't tried it solo, but the named mobs sometimes summon and the add range is high, but pulling to middle or sw corner zone wall its very easy to get singles....I suppose you could chant kite and charm fight there as well, I don't think you could easily swarm, but now that I mention it, I might try it with my 52 FV bard some time.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
