				<td colspan="2"><span>your doing real well if have 7k and lambent tons of gear that is way better then lamb is pretty cheap these days.  If your looking to solo katta isnt bad used to be a post here on how to do it basically ya stand on steps hit a guard with a spell and book out fast to front door. Its good exp and good way to learn to swarm if ya havent.  
<br />

<br />
Take ya to 56-57 pretty fast they drop weaps and decent amount of plat average 10-12 pp a mob x ten+ mobs a pull can sell right there too since nathyns house is seperate faction then rest of zone. Repop is slow but if get em all couple usually repop before ya finish em all off.
<br />

<br />
Swarming is fun when ya first start trying though eventually get just as old as chanting when ya master it though.  Ldons are a good place to go if have enough time to group, most people in em anymore are prolly twinks which is good thing for you though I havent played any of my alts in while last time i was on an alt spent long time looking for a healer. 
<br />

<br />
If ya can only play in small blocks id prolly recomend soloing to 60ish atleast the majority of the fast to form ldon groups are 65 ish tho that may have changed since oow cant say i have done one in 8 months or so hehe.  Still good source tho get a cleric and tank friend or 2 can pretty much fill out a ldon group with whatever else.</span></td>
